{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia\n\nSCIALLINO 40 FLY. RENT A MOTORBOAT IN SARDINIA.\n\nThe Sciallino 40 Fly features 3 spacious cabins and 2 bathrooms. The love for sailing is satisfied with this vessel, which, while maintaining its classic character, offers sleeker lines and planing hulls, always aiming for exceptional sea performance. With large interior spaces, where wood adds an elegant and classic touch, the Sciallino 40 Fly consists of a majestic dinette with a comfortable sofa next to the internal helm area, a fully equipped kitchen, and a complete bathroom. Two well-appointed guest cabins feature large wooden wardrobes, and a refined master cabin with a complete bathroom and shower allows guests to enjoy the interior spaces with the utmost comfort aboard this motorboat for rent. Following its classic style, the exterior spaces of this vessel include a large cockpit, a charming bow lounge, and a steering area where you can helm the boat.","blueprint":{"name":"SCIALLINO 40","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::c1edd390-dab5-11f0-b742-69cb5d4aea8e/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::bc738a00-da9b-11f0-bb79-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::bc73b110-da9b-11f0-bb79-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::bc72c6b0-da9b-11f0-bb79-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::bc71dc50-da9b-11f0-bb79-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::bc733be1-da9b-11f0-bb79-250e2e71de59/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bb444b10-da96-11f0-8358-e32d53d7fa58::assets::bc718